align-items_key3: Iss property se hum yeh set karte hai ki flex-items container ke andar kaise height lengi.
align-items_key4: By default iski value stretch hoti hai yaani ki flex-items container mein jitne height unhe chahiye utni height leni ki koshish karte hai.
align-items_key5: Iss example ko dekho aur isme container ki css se align-items:center waali line se comment hata kar dekho ki kya hota hai. Aur align-items ki alag alag value daal kar bhi dekho.
